steps.html_instructions:
Slight left onto Ali Dirikoç Blv./Kayseri Cd./D765
Continue to follow Kayseri Cd./D765
Keep left to continue on Zübeyde Hanım Cd.
Turn right to stay on Kayseri Nevşehir Yolu/D300
Keep left at the fork to continue toward Kayseri Niğde Yolu/D805

Keep right at the fork and merge onto Kayseri Niğde Yolu/D805
Continue to follow Kayseri Niğde Yolu

Continue onto Sivas Yolu/D260
Continue to follow D260

Take the ramp on the left onto Kayseri Sivas Yolu/D850
Continue to follow D850

Take the ramp onto Erzincan-Erzurum Çevre Yolu/D200/E88
Continue to follow D200/E88
Keep left to continue on Sivas Erzincan Yolu
Turn right onto the ramp to Gümüşhane Erzincan Yolu/Kelkit Cd./D885
Keep left at the fork to continue toward Gümüşhane Erzincan Yolu/Kelkit Cd./D885

Continue onto Gümüşhane Erzincan Yolu/Kelkit Cd./D885
Continue to follow Gümüşhane Erzincan Yolu/D885
Demirözü Yolu turns slightly right and becomes Bayburt Demirözü Yolu
